Interface GifProviderProtocol

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GiphyGifProvider, TenorGifProvider

    public interface GifProviderProtocol
    Created by Keval on 19-Aug-17. Protocol to implement GIFs provider. Create an adapter to integrate different GIF services like GIPHY or Tenor.
